item.description:
Hello All-

It's that time, time for you to get your best - most interesting photo - print it and bring it to the Photo Critique Night!! Share with fellow meetup photogs, give feedback and learn what you can...

Yes these must be prints to share and pass around the table or to stand on an easel... No computers! Please bring only 2 PRINTs- no more... WE want to give everyone a turn...

All of this will take place at Don's place- our fabulous hosts home - on Wednesday, July 22 at 7:00 pm at 6 Salisbury Crag, Worcester, MA.

Feel free to bring a snack or drink to share with the group.
item.how_to_find_us: We meet in the parking lot to car pool and get organized...
